{"tid":2462194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港共叫12國唔承認BNO","createTime":"2021-03-26T00:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T06:27:56.000Z","uid":268271,"like":46,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"882e34dc487d6ce2b36447adf43a800caac0bd05","tid":2462194,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明顯干預別國內政<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫英國唔承認BNO先至好笑"},{"pid":"115af5177558c2ad00c66743a190dacec7b44104","tid":2462194,"uid":268271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"882e34dc487d6ce2b36447adf43a800caac0bd05","tid":2462194,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明顯干預別國內政<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫英國唔承認BNO先至好笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:36:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582552-20210325.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582552-20210325.htm&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=dbb7c032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582552-20210325.htm&h=eb39745f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582552-20210325.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bb1870599b79feec35e8ff4ae281c2fe69e195cb","tid":2462194,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:36:52.000Z","msg":"呢12個國家包埋英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4221ea7ab904460d65c2aa23d7a1c43f2a15beda","tid":2462194,"uid":17641,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:38:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>泛民咪一樣叫中共結束一黨專政</strong></span><img